summary:
Adds the Witch Elf race. 
A copy of the Dark Elf race with Caucasian skin tones and altered skills/racial abilities.
descriptionHtml:
Description
===========
Adds the Witch Elf race. 
A copy of the Dark Elf race with Caucasian skin tones and altered skills/racial abilities.

New Racial Abilities:
Witch Speed (power) - Slows Time for 30 seconds
Deadly Poison (active effect) - Poisons applied to weapons lasts for 5 hits (6 with the concentrated poison perk) 

Skills:
Alchemy +10
One handed +10 
Illusion +5
Light armor +5
Sneak +5

Recommended
===========
This mod doesn\'t add any new meshes or textures. The screenshots were taken with these mods:

UNP Female Body >>> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709
Better Males >>> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488
Better Females >>> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812
ApachiiSkyHair >>> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
 
Install
=======
Extract the archive.
Copy \'Witch Elf Race.esp\' to your Skyrim/Data folder.
Don\'t forget to check the data file in the launcher.

Uninstall
=========
Uncheck the data file in the launcher.
Delete \'Witch Elf Race.esp\' from your Skyrim/Data folder.

Updates
=======
31/07/12 - Now supports vampire transformation.
	 - Witch Speed now also increases weapon and movement speed.

Credits
=======
Thanks to:
Bethesda for Skyrim and the CK

Legal
=====
Only vanilla assets were used.
